videos.description: Michigan defense hits the floor for the ball and heaves it up the court to Duncan Robinson for the slam.
videos.headline: Robinson throws down uncontested dunk

videos.description: Northwestern's Scottie Lindsey gets the ball on the wing and drives to the hoop for a jam.
videos.headline: Lindsey drives and dunks

videos.description: Michigan takes the lead for the first time today after a 10-0 run is topped off by a Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Great ball movement leads to Abdur-Rahkman 3

videos.description: Michigan's quick ball movement leaves Moritz Wagner open for the deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Wagner drains deep 3

videos.description: Charles Matthews throws down after taking the ball from Vic Law on transition.
videos.headline: Matthews steals and slams
